text: Ayupovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Yunusovsky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 342 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 11 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye, 10 km from Yunusovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Ayupovo
